cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object pose recovery from depth images using a novel architecture. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the application of the proposed architecture in robotic systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper introduces a new learning-based approach for object pose estimation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also be relevant as the paper proposes a new method for solving a challenging problem in computer vision. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with 3D object registration and visualization.
